Overview
The Flashcard Quiz App is a simple and interactive web application that helps users learn and memorize information using flashcards and quizzes. It supports multiple question types, study modes, and tracks user progress with detailed statistics.
Features
• Create, update, and delete decks of flashcards.
• Support for various question types: flashcard, multiple-choice, true/false, fill-in-the-blank.
• Study mode with optional timed questions and automatic progression.
• Shuffle questions for varied study sessions.
• Track quiz progress, score, and study time.
• Flag cards for review.
• View deck and overall statistics.
Technologies Used
• React (with hooks) for UI
• Wouter for routing
• TanStack Query for data fetching and caching
• TypeScript for type safety
• Custom in-memory storage implementation (MemStorage) to simulate backend
Testing
This project is primarily designed for manual testing to evaluate different testing techniques from a customer perspective.
